[I] A library that parses the file format of FreeHand documents

[T] Libfreehand is a library that parses the file format of
[T] Aldus/Macromedia/Adobe FreeHand documents. It supports documents from
[T] version 3 to 11.

[U] https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/DLP/Libraries/libfreehand

